	<p>All Pets Veterinary Hospital has been a leader in specialty veterinary care since 1990, fulfilling the need
for specialty healthcare and emergency services for animals in San Diego County and Southern
California.</p>
<p><blockquote>No matter how little money and how few possessions you own, having a dog makes you rich.</p>
